# Analytics & Event Tracking Workflow

## Basic Requirements
- Centralize event schemas (name, version, required props); validate before send
- Asynchronous, non-blocking delivery; batch where possible

## Mandatory Actions
- Use semantic event names with domain prefixes (e.g., `product.viewed`)
- Include device/user/session identifiers where legal; honor consent and privacy
- Retry transient failures with backoff; drop or queue offline safely

## Forbidden Behaviors
- Sending PII without hashing or consent; leaking secrets
- Tying UI rendering to tracking completion

## Example Code
```ts
track('product.viewed', { productId, price, currency });
```
